title.text: AI Model Parameters vs Training Dataset Size
title.subtext: Logarithmic scale comparison across different eras

tooltip.formatter:
function(params) { const data = params.data; const params_formatted = (data.parameters / 1e9).toFixed(1) + "B"; const dataset_formatted = (data.dataset_size / 1e12).toFixed(1) + "T"; return data.name + "
" + "Organization: " + (data.organization || "Unknown") + "
" + "Parameters: " + params_formatted + "
" + "Dataset Size: " + dataset_formatted + " tokens
" + "Date: " + (data.publication_date || "Unknown"); }
